trans-unit.source: Provides a way to index and retrieve a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 提供 <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> 物件集合的索引和擷取之方式。

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates the <xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection.AllKeys%2A> property and the <xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection.GetKey%2A> and <xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection.CopyTo%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例示範<xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection.AllKeys%2A>屬性和<xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection.GetKey%2A>和<xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection.CopyTo%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection>類別。

trans-unit.source: The example gets the application object for the current request from the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> object.
trans-unit.target: 此範例會取得目前要求的應用程式物件從目前<xref:System.Web.HttpContext>物件。

trans-unit.source: It then extracts the <xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection> object from the application instance and displays the names of the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> objects.
trans-unit.target: 然後將解壓縮<xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection>從應用程式執行個體的物件，並顯示的名稱<xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>物件。

trans-unit.source: Gets a string array containing all the keys (module names) in the <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 取得字串陣列，包含在 <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection" /> 中所有索引鍵 (模組名稱)。

trans-unit.source: An array of module names.
trans-unit.target: 模組名稱的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates the <xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection.AllKeys%2A> property and the <xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection.GetKey%2A> and <xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection.CopyTo%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection> class.

trans-unit.source: The destination <see cref="T:System.Array" />.
trans-unit.target: 目的地 <see cref="T:System.Array" />。

trans-unit.source: The index of the destination <see cref="T:System.Array" /> where copying starts.
trans-unit.target: 開始複製的目的 <see cref="T:System.Array" /> 索引。

trans-unit.source: Copies members of the module collection to an <see cref="T:System.Array" />, beginning at the specified index of the array.
trans-unit.target: 將模組集合的成員複製到 <see cref="T:System.Array" /> (從陣列的指定索引處開始)。

trans-unit.source: Returns an individual <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> object from the <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 從 <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> 傳回個別 <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection" /> 物件。

trans-unit.target: 要從集合中傳回的 <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> 物件的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> object with the specified index from the <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 以指定索引從 <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> 傳回 <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpModuleCollection" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> member specified by the <paramref name="index" /> parameter.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 參數所指定的 <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> 成員。

trans-unit.target: 要擷取的項目之索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: Index of the key to retrieve from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要從集合中擷取的索引鍵的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the key (name) of the <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> object at the specified numerical index.
trans-unit.target: 傳回指定數值索引處的 <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> 物件之索引鍵 (名稱)。

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> member specified by the <paramref name="index" /> parameter.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 參數所指定的 <see cref="T:System.Web.IHttpModule" /> 成員名稱。
